sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant TS as Trust Server
    participant UE as UE (User Equipment)
    participant eNB as eNB/gNB
    participant CN as Core Network (MME/AMF)

    Note over UE,eNB: Cell Search & System Information
    UE->>eNB: PSS/SSS Synchronization
    eNB-->>UE: Physical Cell ID (PCI)
    UE->>eNB: Read MIB (Master Information Block)
    UE->>eNB: Read SIB1 (System Information Block 1)
    Note over eNB: SIB1 contains Global Cell ID:<br/>PLMN-ID + Cell Identity
    eNB-->>UE: Global Cell ID = "450-05-eNB9999-Cell0"

    Note over UE,TS: Trust Server Query for Untrust Score
    UE->>TS: UNTRUST_SCORE_QUERY<br/>{cell_id: "450-05-eNB9999-Cell0"}
    TS->>TS: Query Database

    alt Score >= 70 (BARRED)
        TS-->>UE: Score = 85, Status = BARRED
        UE->>UE: Reject Cell (FBS Suspected)
    else Score 50-69 (LOW_PRIORITY)
        TS-->>UE: Score = 55, Status = LOW_PRIORITY
        UE->>UE: Mark as Low Priority
    else Score < 50 (TRUSTED)
        TS-->>UE: Score = 15, Status = TRUSTED
        Note over UE,CN: Proceed to Normal Attachment
        UE->>eNB: RRCConnectionRequest
        eNB->>UE: RRCConnectionSetup
        UE->>eNB: RRCConnectionSetupComplete
        UE->>CN: ATTACH REQUEST
        CN->>UE: AKA Authentication
        UE->>CN: Authentication Response
        CN->>UE: Security Mode Command (EEA2/EIA2)
        UE->>CN: Security Mode Complete
        CN->>UE: ATTACH ACCEPT
    end
